## Conclusion

This project demonstrates the end-to-end workflow of a data analyst, beginning with data cleaning in Excel, followed by SQL-based exploration and analysis.
The project highlights how demographic characteristics and geographic location can influence both voting behavior and perceptions of electoral integrity.

The analysis provides a practical example of using SQL to extract insights from survey-based election data while showcasing core data analysis skills applicable to real-world business and research environments.
